1
00:00:33,750 --> 00:00:36,291
[GANTA THINKING]
How can I be so pathetic?

2
00:00:36,375 --> 00:00:41,375
I just... I just stand
there and take it!

3
00:00:41,458 --> 00:00:44,291
You're too weak to
be left on your own!

4
00:00:44,375 --> 00:00:46,166
[GANTA THINKING]
She's got me all figured out.

5
00:00:46,250 --> 00:00:49,125
Meanwhile, I jump to conclusions
and shove her away... 

6
00:00:49,208 --> 00:00:51,916
Then, when shit gets bad,
I want her to save me?!

7
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,250
What the hell...?!

8
00:00:53,333 --> 00:00:56,375
It makes me wanna put my
hand through a damn wall!

9
00:00:59,791 --> 00:01:01,000
[SENJI] Hmm...?

10
00:01:01,083 --> 00:01:02,166
[GANTA BREATHES HEAVILY]

11
00:01:02,250 --> 00:01:04,291
I want you to teach me,
Senji--right now!

12
00:01:04,375 --> 00:01:07,666
I have to learn how to
fight like a real Deadman!

13
00:01:07,750 --> 00:01:11,250
[SENJI] How'm I supposed
to teach a crybaby?

14
00:01:11,333 --> 00:01:13,958
[GANTA]
I have to get stronger...

15
00:01:14,041 --> 00:01:17,375
Strong enough to save Nagi
from that horrible monk...

16
00:01:17,458 --> 00:01:19,250
Strong enough that Shiro
won't have to come to

17
00:01:19,333 --> 00:01:21,750
my rescue all the time!

18
00:01:21,833 --> 00:01:26,125
Strong enough... to avenge
all of my murdered friends!

19
00:01:26,208 --> 00:01:31,291
Strong enough to not feel this
fucking miserable all the time!

20
00:01:31,375 --> 00:01:36,000
I just wanna be strong enough
to kill the Ganta I used to be!

21
00:01:36,083 --> 00:01:42,583
[GANTA CRIES]

22
00:01:42,666 --> 00:01:43,625
Heh...

23
00:01:43,708 --> 00:01:45,250
Not that I don't
dig your reasons...

24
00:01:45,333 --> 00:01:49,166
But... I coulda done
without the waterworks.

25
00:01:49,250 --> 00:01:50,958
I'm sorry...

26
00:01:51,041 --> 00:01:53,458
[SENJI] I short-shrifted
you on that, Igarashi...

27
00:01:53,541 --> 00:01:56,583
You never give up.

28
00:01:56,666 --> 00:01:58,750
Are you sure 'bout this?

29
00:01:58,833 --> 00:02:00,708
Because once the old
you's dead and gone, 

30
00:02:00,791 --> 00:02:04,083
then you gotta own up
to whatever takes its place.

31
00:02:10,083 --> 00:02:11,958
No problem.

32
00:02:16,041 --> 00:02:21,000
♪ opening song ♪

33
00:03:51,208 --> 00:03:52,416
[SHIRO]
Another chocolate!

34
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:53,750
[TOTO]
C'mon, Wretched Egg...

35
00:03:53,833 --> 00:03:55,166
All you've done since yesterday

36
00:03:55,250 --> 00:03:57,166
is stuff your
pretty little face!

37
00:03:57,250 --> 00:03:58,625
What's a
"Wretched Egg"?

38
00:03:58,708 --> 00:04:00,208
Huh? You are, silly!

39
00:04:00,291 --> 00:04:03,500
My name is Shiro,
and don't you forget it!

40
00:04:03,583 --> 00:04:05,750
I still can't believe
your friend hit you...

41
00:04:05,833 --> 00:04:07,791
That must have
been quite a shock.

42
00:04:07,875 --> 00:04:09,541
My cheek
still hurts...!

43
00:04:09,625 --> 00:04:12,166
As if...
You don't hurt.

44
00:04:12,250 --> 00:04:15,541
Aceman is Shiro's
secret identity...

45
00:04:15,625 --> 00:04:20,291
After Shiro turned into Aceman,
nothing could ever hurt her.

46
00:04:20,375 --> 00:04:21,916
But I don't get it...

47
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:26,333
I turned into Aceman
to help him, so...

48
00:04:26,416 --> 00:04:29,083
Why does Ganta
hate me so much?

49
00:04:29,166 --> 00:04:32,041
How come the cookies
don't taste good?

50
00:04:32,125 --> 00:04:36,916
I'm eating and eating, so
how come I feel all empty?

51
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:39,333
Why do I even care?

52
00:04:39,416 --> 00:04:40,791
Huh...?

53
00:04:40,875 --> 00:04:45,375
Ganta's a big baby! So why
does it hurt so much, huh?!

54
00:04:45,458 --> 00:04:48,416
You never felt bad
before. Why bother now?

55
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:50,833
There's no
point to it.

56
00:04:50,916 --> 00:04:52,750
You save his life
time and again...

57
00:04:52,833 --> 00:04:54,166
...and he turns
his back on you!

58
00:04:54,250 --> 00:04:55,666
Filthy ingrate!

59
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:58,458
Guys like him are just so
two-faced and irresponsible...

60
00:04:58,541 --> 00:05:00,000
When they mess up...

61
00:05:00,083 --> 00:05:03,000
you can bet they'll try to pin
the blame on someone else.

62
00:05:03,083 --> 00:05:05,583
Does that sound like a friend
worth blubbering over?

63
00:05:05,666 --> 00:05:07,125
He's not
worth anything!

64
00:05:07,208 --> 00:05:08,916
I hate that
big meanie!

65
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:11,166
It's Ganta's fault
Shiro feels bad!

66
00:05:11,250 --> 00:05:12,916
I'll punch 'em back!

67
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,333
[TOTO]
Hey...! Wait a sec!

68
00:05:15,416 --> 00:05:17,291
[TOTO SIGHS]

69
00:05:20,083 --> 00:05:21,333
Huh...?

70
00:05:24,208 --> 00:05:26,416
Hold on, these chocolates
have liquor in them!

71
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:29,208
And Shiro's been tossing
them back non-stop...

72
00:05:29,291 --> 00:05:30,375
Oh, what the heck...

73
00:05:30,458 --> 00:05:33,166
Not like a single one
is going to hurt.

74
00:05:36,916 --> 00:05:40,083
It tastes like a branch of
sin melting in my mouth!

75
00:05:40,166 --> 00:05:41,291
[TOTO LAUGHS]

76
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:44,500
[KARAKO]
Nagi's on his own now, guys.

77
00:05:44,583 --> 00:05:45,791
We can't just rush the gate,

78
00:05:45,875 --> 00:05:47,833
so we're gonna split
up and sneak out.

79
00:05:47,916 --> 00:05:49,166
Hope we get lucky.

80
00:05:49,250 --> 00:05:50,416
[WAKABAYASHI]
Yeah, but...

81
00:05:50,500 --> 00:05:51,541
the other routes that
we beat out of Rokuro

82
00:05:51,625 --> 00:05:53,291
might not be safe, right?

83
00:05:53,375 --> 00:05:55,666
[KARAKO] Nothing's ever
been safe in this place.

84
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:57,125
[MIYAKO]
What choice do we have?

85
00:05:57,208 --> 00:05:59,041
And if you happen to run
into an Undertaker...

86
00:05:59,125 --> 00:06:01,250
well... good luck with that.

87
00:06:01,333 --> 00:06:02,750
Take it a
step at a time.

88
00:06:02,833 --> 00:06:04,000
So to speak.

89
00:06:04,083 --> 00:06:05,416
Is Ganta coming with us?

90
00:06:05,500 --> 00:06:07,958
Yeah, shouldn't he have
gotten here by now?

91
00:06:08,041 --> 00:06:10,458
[KARAKO]
We can't risk waiting around.

92
00:06:10,541 --> 00:06:13,000
You told the kid
the wrong time, didn'tcha?

93
00:06:13,083 --> 00:06:15,125
Yeah, I thought it
would be better that way.

94
00:06:15,208 --> 00:06:16,708
Y'know he's gonna
hate you for it.

95
00:06:16,791 --> 00:06:18,250
I already put him
through hell once

96
00:06:18,333 --> 00:06:19,916
for thinking he was tougher.

97
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:22,500
I figure he hates me plenty.

98
00:06:22,583 --> 00:06:25,541
He's still young...
He'll get another shot someday.

99
00:06:25,625 --> 00:06:29,833
This ain't going to be easy, but
it's something we got to do.

100
00:06:29,916 --> 00:06:31,916
From scarred to free.

101
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:34,458
[GROUP]
From scarred to free.

102
00:06:39,916 --> 00:06:41,750
[ROKURO]
Quite a send-off, hayseed.

103
00:06:41,833 --> 00:06:42,750
You're alive...?

104
00:06:42,833 --> 00:06:44,500
I guess we didn't
thrash ya 'nuff.

105
00:06:44,583 --> 00:06:49,333
[ROKURO] The odds of you getting
out alive are... 32%, tops.

106
00:06:49,416 --> 00:06:52,416
Two per cent flat, if you
run into an Undertaker.

107
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:54,291
[KARAKO]
They're going to make it out.

108
00:06:54,375 --> 00:06:55,666
C'mon... You're
not really gonna

109
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:58,541
try and take 'em out
yourself, are you...?

110
00:06:58,625 --> 00:07:01,000
That's suicide.

111
00:07:01,083 --> 00:07:03,833
A little bitch can
go a long way. 

112
00:07:03,916 --> 00:07:07,208
They're just gonna kill ya,
you know that, right?

113
00:07:07,291 --> 00:07:10,166
You suck at math,
don'tcha, cunt? 

114
00:07:13,958 --> 00:07:16,833
[NAGI]
It was a gift from my wife...

115
00:07:16,916 --> 00:07:19,458
I wanted to keep a picture
of our child on me.

116
00:07:19,541 --> 00:07:21,500
Is it a girl...?
Or a little boy?

117
00:07:21,583 --> 00:07:23,208
A little girl.

118
00:07:23,291 --> 00:07:25,250
Can I open it?

119
00:07:25,333 --> 00:07:26,875
[NAGI]
By all means.

120
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:30,041
Thanks to her, there's
a light in my heart

121
00:07:30,125 --> 00:07:33,041
that even this vile
place can't snuff out...

122
00:07:33,125 --> 00:07:35,000
One of these days,
the rain will stop,

123
00:07:35,083 --> 00:07:36,750
the clouds will clear...

124
00:07:36,833 --> 00:07:40,416
and a rainbow
will span the sky.

125
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:43,291
I know it sounds corny. Heh...

126
00:07:43,375 --> 00:07:44,875
Adorable, huh?

127
00:07:44,958 --> 00:07:46,625
[NAGI LAUGHS]

128
00:07:46,708 --> 00:07:48,750
Maybe Daddy's biased.

129
00:07:48,833 --> 00:07:49,958
No, you're right...!

130
00:07:50,041 --> 00:07:52,750
She looks a lot like
her Daddy, in fact.

131
00:08:05,708 --> 00:08:07,500
[GANTA YELLS]

132
00:08:07,583 --> 00:08:09,500
[SENJI] That's twelve times
I've killed your ass!

133
00:08:09,583 --> 00:08:12,333
You're too slow!
And your shot is totally weak.

134
00:08:12,416 --> 00:08:13,708
Not to mention
you're telegraphing

135
00:08:13,791 --> 00:08:15,666
the shot-path
like a motherfucker.

136
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:17,000
But it's all moot, anyway,

137
00:08:17,083 --> 00:08:19,166
'cause you're still not
firing faster than sound.

138
00:08:19,250 --> 00:08:20,750
[GANTA]
Faster than sound...?

139
00:08:20,833 --> 00:08:23,041
[SENJI] Look, that's your blood,
man, so you call the shots...!

140
00:08:23,125 --> 00:08:24,625
You gotta start thinking
of that shit as

141
00:08:24,708 --> 00:08:26,166
an extension of yourself.

142
00:08:26,250 --> 00:08:29,250
[GANTA] Yeah...! Yeah, I do,
but it's not helping any.

143
00:08:29,333 --> 00:08:31,916
[SENJI] Hold on... You happen
to have any candy on ya?

144
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:35,708
[GANTA] Huh...? Oh...
yeah, right in here...

145
00:08:40,375 --> 00:08:41,541
[GANTA YELLS]

146
00:08:41,625 --> 00:08:43,750
Senji! What the hell did
you crush my candy for?!

147
00:08:43,833 --> 00:08:46,166
[SENJI]
Hold it, noob!

148
00:08:46,250 --> 00:08:48,875
Shoot it down, and
you can have it back.

149
00:08:48,958 --> 00:08:52,000
But I'm gonna
cockblock all your shots.

150
00:08:52,083 --> 00:08:53,833
You had just better
hope that your Ganta Gun

151
00:08:53,916 --> 00:08:56,250
is faster than my
Invisible Black...

152
00:08:56,333 --> 00:08:58,708
Y'know... if you
wanna live, an' shit.

153
00:08:58,791 --> 00:09:01,125
You're gonna improve
real fuckin' quick.

154
00:09:01,208 --> 00:09:04,375
that or you're gonna die...
So let'er rip, kid.

155
00:09:15,041 --> 00:09:16,125
[GANTA YELLS]

156
00:09:24,291 --> 00:09:26,291
Not even close!

157
00:09:26,375 --> 00:09:27,916
Again, dammit!

158
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,666
What, are you
asleep over there?!

159
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:31,875
[TOTO LAUGHS]

160
00:09:31,958 --> 00:09:32,708
[SENJI GASPS]

161
00:09:32,791 --> 00:09:33,833
Fuck,
it's you...

162
00:09:33,916 --> 00:09:36,250
Hi there... Do you
know where Shiro is?

163
00:09:36,333 --> 00:09:37,750
The Mockingbird!

164
00:09:37,833 --> 00:09:40,041
She ran off yelling about
how she had to punch someone.

165
00:09:40,125 --> 00:09:42,833
Some guy named Ganta,
I think it was...?

166
00:09:42,916 --> 00:09:46,083
Are you...
a friend of Shiro's?

167
00:09:46,166 --> 00:09:48,041
Long time no see,
old buddy...

168
00:09:48,125 --> 00:09:49,375
I like the eye-patch!

169
00:09:49,458 --> 00:09:52,000
Man, you vanished without
a trace, Mockingbird...

170
00:09:52,083 --> 00:09:54,208
So what the hell've
you been up to?

171
00:09:54,291 --> 00:09:57,000
Sorry 'bout that!
I was dead for a little while!

172
00:09:57,083 --> 00:09:57,750
Huh?!

173
00:09:57,833 --> 00:09:59,208
[SENJI YELLS]

174
00:10:04,583 --> 00:10:05,625
[TOTO LAUGHS]

175
00:10:05,708 --> 00:10:07,416
I don't wanna
fight you, Senji...

176
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:10,500
between the two of us,
I'm madly in love with you!

177
00:10:10,583 --> 00:10:13,625
Ew... God, you weren't
like this before...

178
00:10:16,250 --> 00:10:18,375
Hey! You keep your
tongue away from me!

179
00:10:18,458 --> 00:10:20,250
Uh... what's the
deal with this guy?

180
00:10:20,333 --> 00:10:22,000
Meet Mockingbird.

181
00:10:22,083 --> 00:10:24,625
He's the strongest
Deadman in Wonderland...

182
00:10:24,708 --> 00:10:26,166
...and totally nuts.

183
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:30,958
[TOTO]
That may have been true once.

184
00:10:31,041 --> 00:10:34,291
But right now I'm probably
the weakest of the bunch!

185
00:10:34,375 --> 00:10:37,791
Easy, Crow, it was
just one taste.

186
00:10:37,875 --> 00:10:40,125
Can you spare a lick?

187
00:10:40,208 --> 00:10:41,125
Huh?!

188
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:45,916
I promise I'll be
gentle with you.

189
00:10:49,416 --> 00:10:51,583
I'm training Ganta
here how to fight better...

190
00:10:51,666 --> 00:10:54,750
so he's gonna need every
last drop of blood he's got.

191
00:10:54,833 --> 00:10:56,750
[TOTO]
Oh, well that is a shame.

192
00:10:56,833 --> 00:10:58,625
Somethin' tells me the chick
you're trying to find

193
00:10:58,708 --> 00:11:00,750
isn't just gonna pop
into the rec room...

194
00:11:00,833 --> 00:11:02,583
Go look
somewhere else.

195
00:11:03,333 --> 00:11:06,500
[TOTO]
Hmm... So, you're him...

196
00:11:06,583 --> 00:11:08,083
Most people call
me the Mockingbird,

197
00:11:08,166 --> 00:11:09,708
but my name is Toto...

198
00:11:09,791 --> 00:11:12,833
It's a pleasure to meet you.

199
00:11:12,916 --> 00:11:14,458
Call me Ganta.

200
00:11:14,541 --> 00:11:17,458
[TOTO] I'll see ya
around... Woodpecker.

201
00:11:17,541 --> 00:11:19,625
Wait up...
Where's Shiro?

202
00:11:20,083 --> 00:11:21,708
[TOTO LAUGHS]

203
00:11:25,041 --> 00:11:32,750
♪ Classical Music ♪

204
00:11:32,833 --> 00:11:34,500
[TAMAKI] It looks as though
you haven't swatted

205
00:11:34,583 --> 00:11:37,833
every last mosquito,
dear Genkaku.

206
00:11:37,916 --> 00:11:40,375
[GENKAKU] Then they'll make
for good target practice.

207
00:11:40,458 --> 00:11:42,750
[TAMAKI] Heh...
Wearing the hats of both

208
00:11:42,833 --> 00:11:46,166
promoter and director
now is hectic.

209
00:11:46,250 --> 00:11:49,958
And there are those with whom
I'm anxious to share my toys.

210
00:11:50,041 --> 00:11:53,291
Please, kill those rebels
just as soon as you can.

211
00:11:53,375 --> 00:11:56,750
Roger wilco,
Mr. Director, sir.

212
00:11:56,833 --> 00:11:59,125
[GENKAKU LAUGHS]

213
00:11:59,208 --> 00:12:02,166
I got all I wanted
out of 'em, anyway.

214
00:12:05,541 --> 00:12:07,416
[ELITE GUARD 11-A YELLS]

215
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:09,125
[ELITE GUARD 11-A]
I'm begging you...!

216
00:12:09,208 --> 00:12:13,541
[ELITE GUARD 11-A SCREAMS]

217
00:12:13,625 --> 00:12:16,125
[TAMAKI] Huh...?
What's that racket?

218
00:12:16,208 --> 00:12:17,708
[GENKAKU] Nothing.

219
00:12:17,791 --> 00:12:21,166
Merely the blossoming
of something red.

220
00:12:33,375 --> 00:12:36,000
[ELITE GUARD 11-B]
What's Genkaku up to in there?

221
00:12:36,083 --> 00:12:38,500
[ELITE GUARD 11-C]
I dunno, but he locked the door.

222
00:12:38,583 --> 00:12:41,250
[ELITE GUARD 11-D] And Satou
hasn't come out yet, has he...?

223
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,333
[KARAKO]
Stay calm, girl...!

224
00:12:50,416 --> 00:12:52,666
From here on out, you're
gonna have to improvise!

225
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:54,208
Just hang on, Nagi!

226
00:12:56,833 --> 00:12:59,291
[KARAKO] What? Oh, shit...
Isn't that...?!

227
00:12:59,375 --> 00:13:01,041
Hullooooo...

228
00:13:01,125 --> 00:13:02,750
[ELITE GUARD 11-B]
Is she with Scar Chain?!

229
00:13:02,833 --> 00:13:03,958
[ELITE GUARD 11-C]
Who the hell're you?!

230
00:13:04,041 --> 00:13:08,041
Huh...? Where am I?
I took the wrong vent...

231
00:13:08,125 --> 00:13:09,333
[KARAKO]
What are you doing in here?!

232
00:13:09,416 --> 00:13:11,625
Are you trying to
get yourself killed?!

233
00:13:11,708 --> 00:13:15,041
[GENKAKU] Why the hell are you
guys being so goddamn loud?

234
00:13:15,125 --> 00:13:18,958
Lookie here, the pasty 
bitch who broke my guitar.

235
00:13:19,041 --> 00:13:21,291
[KARAKO]
Uh... I think she got lost.

236
00:13:21,375 --> 00:13:23,000
I'll drag her back to
where she belongs...!

237
00:13:23,083 --> 00:13:24,375
[GENKAKU]
Yeah, about that...

238
00:13:24,458 --> 00:13:25,375
[KARAKO YELLS]

239
00:13:28,208 --> 00:13:29,416
[ELITE GUARDS GASP]

240
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:31,458
[GENKAKU] Why, here's a
nice, juicy mosquito...!

241
00:13:31,541 --> 00:13:34,750
Buzzing in my ear...
trying to be tricky.

242
00:13:34,833 --> 00:13:38,958
[GENKAKU LAUGHS]

243
00:13:39,708 --> 00:13:40,875
[GANTA GRUNTS]

244
00:13:43,166 --> 00:13:46,583
Tick-tock, Ganta...
Any minute now, am I right?

245
00:13:46,666 --> 00:13:48,375
[GANTA] No! I've still
got a whole hour!

246
00:13:48,458 --> 00:13:50,000
C'mon, I'm still good!

247
00:13:50,083 --> 00:13:51,166
[SENJI]
We're done...

248
00:13:51,250 --> 00:13:54,000
If you pass out now,
you're dead meat...

249
00:13:54,083 --> 00:13:55,916
And you're gonna.

250
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,458
[GANTA]
Dammit, Senji!

251
00:13:57,541 --> 00:13:59,500
Even if you join 'em
on their big adventure,

252
00:13:59,583 --> 00:14:02,791
you'll just get in the way
and be first one to die...

253
00:14:02,875 --> 00:14:06,416
Don't kick life to
the curb... It's stupid.

254
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:08,250
Son of a...!

255
00:14:08,333 --> 00:14:10,375
[GANTA GRUNTS]

256
00:14:10,458 --> 00:14:11,416
[SENJI] Huh?

257
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:16,750
Again...!

258
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:21,583
[GANTA THINKING]
No use... It's too small!

259
00:14:21,666 --> 00:14:23,500
I don't have enough blood!

260
00:14:29,375 --> 00:14:32,791
[EXPLOSION]

261
00:14:36,583 --> 00:14:38,916
Yeah...! Now we're talkin'!

262
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,916
[GANTA GRUNTS]

263
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:43,041
Runnin' on fumes...

264
00:14:46,750 --> 00:14:49,458
[GENKAKU]
Hey, is this thing on?

265
00:14:49,541 --> 00:14:53,000
What's up, you
Scar Chain cocksuckers?!

266
00:14:53,083 --> 00:14:55,000
It's the monk!

267
00:14:55,083 --> 00:14:57,500
[GENKAKU] You still haven't
learned the lesson of the day...

268
00:14:57,583 --> 00:15:00,000
Resignation is
enlightenment, kids!

269
00:15:00,083 --> 00:15:00,791
[GENKAKU LAUGHS]

270
00:15:00,875 --> 00:15:02,375
But enough Buddha for now.

271
00:15:02,458 --> 00:15:04,708
You know, shit like
tag and hide-and-seek

272
00:15:04,791 --> 00:15:07,041
was never my forte.

273
00:15:07,125 --> 00:15:10,000
But gang-rape?!
That one's loads of fun!

274
00:15:10,083 --> 00:15:11,291
[GENKAKU LAUGHS]

275
00:15:11,375 --> 00:15:12,833
I'm gonna give you guys

276
00:15:12,916 --> 00:15:15,000
a "choose your own
adventure" death.

277
00:15:15,083 --> 00:15:19,833
Do you die trying to save the
chicks, or die trying to escape?

278
00:15:19,916 --> 00:15:21,625
[KARAKO] Don't you
dare come after us!

279
00:15:21,708 --> 00:15:24,000
Get to the outside and
show 'em the truth!

280
00:15:24,083 --> 00:15:25,875
Ignore this asshole!

281
00:15:25,958 --> 00:15:26,916
Shiro!

282
00:15:32,041 --> 00:15:35,291
That final shot...
was the shit, Ganta.

283
00:15:35,375 --> 00:15:36,916
Ganta Gun Mark II...!

284
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:39,416
Go fuck 'em up, dead center!

285
00:15:49,833 --> 00:15:53,041
She went alone...
Son of a bitch...! 

286
00:15:55,416 --> 00:15:58,208
[OHARA]
That girl is so stupid!

287
00:15:58,291 --> 00:15:59,750
Oh Karako...!

288
00:15:59,833 --> 00:16:01,333
[OOSHIMA CRIES]

289
00:16:02,625 --> 00:16:07,666
We can't get outta here...
if we... try an' save 'em...!

290
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:09,541
[SHIRO YELLS]

291
00:16:09,625 --> 00:16:10,833
Then we save them!

292
00:16:10,916 --> 00:16:13,083
[OHARA YELLS]

293
00:16:13,875 --> 00:16:15,333
Karako!

294
00:16:20,791 --> 00:16:22,625
[GANTA THINKING]
Which way do I go to get there?!

295
00:16:22,708 --> 00:16:23,875
Shit!

296
00:16:23,958 --> 00:16:25,916
Karako and the others
left me behind!

297
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:29,000
They must have thought I'd be
useless if we got in a fight!

298
00:16:29,083 --> 00:16:30,583
And now Shiro's--!

299
00:16:32,958 --> 00:16:34,458
Get offa me!

300
00:16:35,666 --> 00:16:36,833
[GANTA YELLS]

301
00:16:38,041 --> 00:16:39,375
[GANTA SCREAMS]

302
00:16:39,458 --> 00:16:41,000
[ELITE GUARD 11-E] That's
enough out of you, fucker.

303
00:16:41,083 --> 00:16:42,541
Stand down!

304
00:16:43,833 --> 00:16:45,833
[BUZZING]

305
00:16:45,916 --> 00:16:48,791
[ELITE GUARDS YELL]

306
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:54,708
[MINATSUKI]
Faster-than-light attacks

307
00:16:54,791 --> 00:16:56,666
kick some serious ass, yeah?

308
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:58,791
Huh...? Huh?!

309
00:16:58,875 --> 00:17:00,250
What are you doing here?

310
00:17:00,333 --> 00:17:01,916
If you're looking for
the Undertaker base,

311
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:04,250
it's a little
farther that way.

312
00:17:04,333 --> 00:17:05,500
Look at ya...

313
00:17:05,583 --> 00:17:07,333
Running off into battle
when you don't even know

314
00:17:07,416 --> 00:17:10,416
where the bad guys are.

315
00:17:10,500 --> 00:17:13,208
Now we're even for
my penalty haircut.

316
00:17:13,291 --> 00:17:15,416
Minatsuki... you
gotta come with me!

317
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:18,750
[MINATSUKI] Owl's big jailbreak
doesn't sound like much fun...

318
00:17:18,833 --> 00:17:20,583
And I gotta watch
out for my stupid

319
00:17:20,666 --> 00:17:22,541
non-Deadman brother in here...

320
00:17:22,625 --> 00:17:26,875
'Sides, I'm actually guilty
of what they busted me for.

321
00:17:27,625 --> 00:17:29,083
No, you're not...

322
00:17:29,166 --> 00:17:32,583
Maybe you killed him, but
you're not guilty of anything.

323
00:17:32,666 --> 00:17:34,916
I won't forget
what you did for me.

324
00:17:40,416 --> 00:17:41,875
Dumbass.

325
00:17:46,791 --> 00:17:49,500
[ENDOU YELLS]

326
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:52,250
[OOSHIMA YELLS]

327
00:17:55,333 --> 00:17:58,000
[SHIRO YELLS]

328
00:17:58,083 --> 00:18:01,666
[KARAKO THINKING] Please,
please... let 'em escape!

329
00:18:03,875 --> 00:18:04,916
Ganta!

330
00:18:05,916 --> 00:18:07,250
[GUNS COCK]

331
00:18:07,333 --> 00:18:11,083
Karako...! Shiro...!
I came here to save you!

332
00:18:11,166 --> 00:18:12,791
Ganta...

333
00:18:16,250 --> 00:18:20,416
Shiro doesn't wanna be
saved by a meanie!

334
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:22,875
You bastards!

335
00:18:22,958 --> 00:18:25,041
Stand down, kid!
They'll kill ya!

336
00:18:26,791 --> 00:18:27,791
[ELITE GUARD 11-F]
Try it, dumbass!

337
00:18:27,875 --> 00:18:29,916
That shit doesn't work on us!

338
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:33,541
Gotta launch it
high-velocity... like before!

339
00:18:40,583 --> 00:18:42,583
[ELITE GUARDS YELL]

340
00:18:42,666 --> 00:18:44,083
Bullseye!

341
00:18:44,166 --> 00:18:45,083
[KARAKO] Ganta!

342
00:18:45,166 --> 00:18:46,750
[SHIRO] Oh no!

343
00:18:46,833 --> 00:18:51,000
Shiro...
are you... okay...?

344
00:18:51,083 --> 00:18:52,458
[SHIRO] Ganta...!

345
00:18:56,916 --> 00:18:58,833
Ganta!

346
00:19:11,375 --> 00:19:14,541
[HIBANA] You had a job to
do, but came here instead.

347
00:19:14,625 --> 00:19:16,916
You're such a bad little boy.

348
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:18,458
[HIBANA LAUGHS]

349
00:19:20,291 --> 00:19:23,375
Everyone else ran...
like you told 'em.

350
00:19:23,458 --> 00:19:27,916
That's why...
I came to... save...!

351
00:19:30,416 --> 00:19:32,833
[GENKAKU]
Just one measly brat...?

352
00:19:32,916 --> 00:19:35,083
I'm a little let down, guys.

353
00:19:35,166 --> 00:19:37,125
I guess they really
were serious about

354
00:19:37,208 --> 00:19:39,625
blowing this taco stand...

355
00:19:39,708 --> 00:19:43,583
It doesn't look like any other
Scar Chain are gonna roll in.

356
00:19:43,666 --> 00:19:44,791
Well fuck it...

357
00:19:44,875 --> 00:19:47,833
Whaddya say we get this
gig started already?

358
00:19:47,916 --> 00:19:52,875
[GUITAR SOUNDS]

359
00:20:06,291 --> 00:20:07,375
[KARAKO GASPS]

360
00:20:07,458 --> 00:20:09,875
Who the hell is that?

361
00:20:09,958 --> 00:20:11,125
Nagi!

362
00:20:11,208 --> 00:20:14,125
[NAGI] Don't come any
closer! I'm begging you!

363
00:20:16,208 --> 00:20:19,916
I've been asleep...
but I just woke up.

364
00:20:25,708 --> 00:20:28,833
Nagi, please hurry up!
We gotta go right now...!

365
00:20:28,916 --> 00:20:31,416
Because your daughter
is waiting for you!

366
00:20:31,500 --> 00:20:33,250
Is she, now...?

367
00:20:33,333 --> 00:20:39,583
[NAGI LAUGHS MANIACALLY]

368
00:20:39,666 --> 00:20:40,916
Nagi...?

369
00:20:45,208 --> 00:20:47,958
[NAGI]
That locket is empty.

370
00:20:48,041 --> 00:20:51,916
Genkaku slit my pregnant wife
like a peach, and she died...

371
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:54,583
They both died...

372
00:20:54,666 --> 00:21:00,583
Our baby didn't magically
survive that moment, Karako!

373
00:21:00,666 --> 00:21:04,166
Hatred's been burning
in my soul ever since!

374
00:21:04,250 --> 00:21:08,541
I lost them both...
mother and child...!

375
00:21:10,083 --> 00:21:13,708
[TAMAKI] I really must apologize
for what I've done to you, Nagi.

376
00:21:13,791 --> 00:21:16,916
Trust me, no one feels
worse about this than I do.

377
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:21,750
But in order to
make an omelette...

378
00:21:21,833 --> 00:21:24,708
...you have to
break a few eggs.

379
00:21:32,416 --> 00:21:34,833
[NAGI GROWLS ANGRILY]

380
00:21:38,750 --> 00:21:41,333
[NAGI LAUGHS MANIACALLY]

381
00:21:41,416 --> 00:21:44,041
[NAGI] My daughter and I
were going to be reunited.

382
00:21:44,125 --> 00:21:46,625
A nice dream,
huh--but I woke up.

383
00:21:46,708 --> 00:21:48,875
And now I that
I know it's all bullshit,

384
00:21:48,958 --> 00:21:51,125
I remember how much
I hate everyone!

385
00:21:51,208 --> 00:21:52,500
Why'm I still alive?

386
00:21:52,583 --> 00:21:54,500
Why are any of
us still alive?!

387
00:21:54,583 --> 00:21:58,083
Why do they deserve to
live while my baby died?!

388
00:21:58,166 --> 00:22:02,291
[NAGI SCREAMS]

389
00:22:05,041 --> 00:22:06,208
Nagi...

390
00:22:11,291 --> 00:22:15,041
I hate the very flesh
I'm trapped inside of...

391
00:22:15,125 --> 00:22:22,125
[NAGI SOBS]

392
00:22:24,041 --> 00:22:28,000
[EXPLOSION]

393
00:22:28,083 --> 00:22:28,958
Don't do this!

394
00:22:29,041 --> 00:22:32,958
[MULTIPLE EXPLOSIONS]

395
00:22:44,083 --> 00:22:46,083
[GENKAKU LAUGHS]

396
00:22:46,166 --> 00:22:49,041
Why settle for an owl when
you can be a vulture...?

397
00:22:49,125 --> 00:22:51,000
Right, love?

398
00:22:51,083 --> 00:22:55,041
Kill 'em all, Nagi!
Show 'em the light!

399
00:22:55,125 --> 00:22:58,375
[NAGI GROWLS ANGRILY]

400
00:23:00,208 --> 00:23:06,250
[NAGI SCREAMS]

401
00:23:08,166 --> 00:23:13,125
♪ closing song ♪

402
00:24:39,250 --> 00:24:42,250
[MAKINA] Even powerlessness is
more than most people can muster

403
00:24:42,333 --> 00:24:44,500
in the face of true despair.

404
00:24:44,583 --> 00:24:46,625
The abyss is a calm place,

405
00:24:46,708 --> 00:24:49,500
and some people mistake
that for salvation.

406
00:24:49,583 --> 00:24:53,125
If you're one of 'em,
Ganta--just stay down.

